{"id": 1874, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你都见过哪些对“自由”的误解？", "description": "“言论自由是一个人跟政府之间的事，而不是他跟另一个普通人之间的事。”——@老刘在德克萨斯", "record_count": 14907, "comment_count": 50, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170828124616Rw4KshFlqjPCA1Za.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-28T17:00:36Z", "questions": [{"id": 2865, "title": "现如今，你都见过哪些对“自由”的误解？", "content": "现如今，你都见过哪些对“自由”的误解？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 232035, "content": "滥用，把下载盗版当做分享自由，“好东西应该让更多人看到”", "image": "img/option/option/2017082817392436sOkqHpoYTSA0jN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231883, "content": "对象错误，把言论自由当作“我有在社交网络骂任何人”的自由", "image": "img/option/option/20170828125429FEU2gZA1snkXSub4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231884, "content": "基本概念错误，如果质疑国家或爱国主义，“你就不配拥有言论自由”", "image": "img/option/option/201708281255320I9aOFsGSnHzUD6f.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231885, "content": "标准单一：比如把责任和自由对立，还被工作羁绊就不配拥有灵魂的自由", "image": "img/option/option/20170828125621oAkTtF1sZzi5dPy4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231887, "content": "混淆原则，将抄袭与致敬借鉴混淆，将恋童和恋爱自由混淆", "image": "img/option/option/20170828125810DiWkz0UxR26Y1Zom.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231888, "content": "重点错，只敢要追求音乐梦想的自由，而非“在歌词里写任何东西的自由”", "image": "img/option/option/20170828130036lXp5A6U0tRkijoFS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231891, "content": "话语宏大忽视日常，比如很少讨论“我们为什么没有在B站看动漫的自由”", "image": "img/option/option/20170828174339qKP09Y73xIMncWCZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231892, "content": "简单化，什么都抬扛，把单纯的反对当自由", "image": "img/option/option/20170828130559WT8AciVUo2OxudCb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}